text: Loverboy is a 2011 Romanian Swedish Serbian drama movie directed by Cătălin Mitulescu and starring George Piştereanu, Ada Condeescu, Ion Besoiu, Clara Vodă, Bogdan Dumitrache, Coca Bloos, Remus Mărgineanu, Adina Galupa. ==Other websites== * Category:2011 drama movies Category:Romanian drama movies Category:Swedish drama movies Category:Serbian movies Category:Movies directed by Cătălin Mitulescu
